HEADWORD: Glossiness
<hw>Gloss"i*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Glossy</er>.]</ety>
<def>The condition or quality of being glossy; the luster or brightness
of a smooth surface.</def> <rj><au>Boyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
